        h2.header-1 How are backups handled?
        p Full backups of every client system are run daily during non-core hours. These backups are kept for 80 days, with no additional storage costs. CaseWare Cloud strictly adheres to their <a href="http://www.casewarecloud.com/pdf/CaseWare%20Cloud%20Privacy%20Policy.pdf" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a> to protect all data and backups.
